                                    • 热设计建议
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 成本分析 -->
                            <div class="ai-function-card" onclick="selectAIFunction('cost-analysis')">
                                <div class="ai-function-icon">💰</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-title">成本优化分析</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-desc">分析器件成本构成和优化建议</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-features">
                                    • 价格趋势分析<br>
                                    • 批量采购建议<br>
                                    • 成本优化方案
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 选型对比 -->
                            <div class="ai-function-card" onclick="selectAIFunction('selection-comparison')">
                                <div class="ai-function-icon">⚖️</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-title">选型对比分析</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-desc">对比多个器件，给出最优选型建议</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-features">
                                    • 多维度参数对比<br>
                                    • 性价比分析<br>
                                    • 选型决策建议
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 技术规格解读 -->
                            <div class="ai-function-card" onclick="selectAIFunction('spec-interpretation')">
                                <div class="ai-function-icon">📖</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-title">技术规格解读</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-desc">深度解读数据手册中的技术规格</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-features">
                                    • 参数含义说明<br>
                                    • 测试条件解析<br>
                                    • 使用限制说明
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 供应链分析 -->
                            <div class="ai-function-card" onclick="selectAIFunction('supply-chain')">
                                <div class="ai-function-icon">🌐</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-title">供应链分析</div>
