                                    • 停产风险预警
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- PDF数据手册智能解读 -->
                            <div class="ai-function-card" onclick="selectAIFunction('pdf-datasheet-analysis')" style="border: 2px solid #00890b; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #f1f8f4 100%);">
                                <div style="position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; background: #00890b; color: white; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;">NEW</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-icon">📄</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-title" style="color: #00890b;">PDF数据手册智能解读</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-desc">上传元器件PDF数据手册，AI智能解读全部内容</div>
                                <div class="ai-function-features">
                                    • 自动识别PDF内容<br>
